    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six. This example features a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-locked limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS top-end refresh and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate chassis fatigue. The engine maintains excellent compression and has been upgraded with VAC coated rod bearings for long-term reliability. The suspension is fitted with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed bushings, ensuring the chassis stays composed under heavy lateral load. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain integrity remain sharp for the purist enthusiast.",
